{"tid":1832151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［1430東區法院支援］劉穎匡今日東區上庭 預料不能保釋","createTime":"2020-01-21T03:18:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T04:18:59.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b37975a41f8ed39349554bfc8221d2c7dafc04","tid":1832151,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:18:47.000Z","msg":"⚠️⚠️劉頴匡被捕跟進⚠️⚠️<br />\n<br />\n律師剛確認，劉頴匡將於今日（21/1）下午兩時三十分於東區法院上庭認訊。<br />\n<br />\n惟律師表示仍未清楚以哪一條控罪起訴，但由於劉有另一單官司在身，頗大機會保釋失敗，需即時還押。<br />\n<br />\n請各位到場聲援。<br />\n<br />\n民間集會團隊<br />\n2020年1月21日"},{"pid":"e7b174a6c3263683e6348beae6215e2084a589d5","tid":1832151,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:36:22.000Z","msg":"推推推推"},{"pid":"66d3b9191cf147402df68db6c58daee0cfe392e7","tid":1832151,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:36:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17877f7a008a43e8161d34f7a0d69517e2ebd658","tid":1832151,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:40:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"371047f8de72b377c37e3533db1e94bb645dec43","tid":1832151,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:55:46.000Z","msg":"屌佢<br />\n真係好撚屈機<br />\n保釋個時是但整條莫須有<br />\n就要還押<br />\n審得黎都已經坐完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (2月尾先審垃圾會個單 當判兩個月 到時出番黎都已經坐完)"},{"pid":"7b64a47e400fd42435e9dc6d3eb3377c273685e4","tid":1832151,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:56:17.000Z","msg":"依家咁既時勢，保釋緊既人真係出街都隨時變還押"},{"pid":"c7761e8292e9beb49b9f5a031492b7034a7bfd93","tid":1832151,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:05:00.000Z","msg":"2月21號先審垃圾會個單<br />\n就算一個月內出到結果<br />\n都已經坐左兩個月<br />\n即係已經坐左最高刑期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\"